Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.66,0:04:56.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而万一我没有回来的话..
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.76,0:04:59.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到那时你就一个人逃走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.44,0:05:10.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被骗了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.10,0:05:12.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全被骗了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.03,0:05:15.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全没有听说还有下次
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.31,0:05:18.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扮成同志来接近我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.94,0:05:20.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是为了让我登上那个沃克先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.04,0:05:24.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那..那段记忆也是骗人的？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.27,0:05:33.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 那是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.78,0:05:35.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概..
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.54,0:05:38.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我弄错了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.71,0:05:41.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪一个是对的？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.07,0:05:45.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我弄不明白啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.30,0:05:53.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 全是姐姐打来的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.79,0:05:54.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.09,0:05:59.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊..没信号
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.59,0:06:02.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦..有了一格
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.14,0:06:06.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔..又没了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.56,0:06:08.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.64,0:06:20.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.52,0:06:22.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学姐的堂妹..
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.35,0:06:26.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后算是打败了那个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.53,0:06:41.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以失去行动能力这一点来讲看来是这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.62,0:06:42.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.11,0:06:45.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说堂妹小姐成功驾驭了它？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.79,0:06:48.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明应该只会骑脚踏车才对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.50,0:06:51.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难不成她有了助动车驾照？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.25,0:06:53.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用那种东西哪有可能开得动机器人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.44,0:06:55.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们说的可是里面的那帮家伙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.87,0:06:58.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们一定藏着什么秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.45,0:07:03.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和花费五年还没从那块零件上找到任何线索的我们不同..
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.82,0:07:07.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里的人只用了半年就把它改造成了机器人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.78,0:07:10.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定有什么秘密..
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.03,0:07:13.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那..那个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.86,0:07:19.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你留在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.22,0:07:20.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.08,0:07:23.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 请别把我一个人留在这种地方
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.19,0:07:30.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果京乃圆没能驾驭沃克斯·奥拉你打算怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.19,0:07:30.08,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(735,660)}vox aura
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.89,0:07:31.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对沃克斯来说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.89,0:07:31.62,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(616,660)}vox
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.62,0:07:34.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,记忆过的搭乘人员是独一无二的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.68,0:07:38.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算沃克斯·奥拉被敌人抢走
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.68,0:07:38.30,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(595,660)}vox aura
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.82,0:07:40.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要死守京乃圆小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.82,0:07:41.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我方就不会落于下风
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.29,0:07:44.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相反就算丢了京乃圆只要守住沃克斯·奥拉情况也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.86,0:07:50.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然还有一种方法是强制促进与沃克斯的活体感应
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.86,0:07:50.50,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(844,660)}vox
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.57,0:07:52.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是稍微有些危险性
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.92,0:07:54.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我想尽可能避免采用这个手段
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.79,0:07:59.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总而言之 就是说其实我手上也没什么很有用的策略
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.61,0:08:02.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是帮了我大忙了 那东西能成功被人驾驭..
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.48,0:08:05.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托您的福我方也非常清楚了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.15,0:08:11.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的脑袋里根本没有保护这个星球的概念
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.08,0:08:15.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保护沃克斯等同于保护地球
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.08,0:08:15.58,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(522,660)}vox
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.42,0:08:19.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让那个沃克斯在最前线拼命的又是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.42,0:08:19.93,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(453,660)}vox
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.56,0:08:23.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因为地球的兵器无法跟他们对抗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.54,0:08:25.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道就没有让那个所谓的沃克斯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.54,0:08:25.04,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(894,660)}vox
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.16,0:08:27.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶紧离开地球这个选择项吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.92,0:08:32.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样一来 地球就会纳入他们的势力范围之内
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.28,0:08:34.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球的未来会是场悲剧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.57,0:08:35.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,够了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.33,0:08:37.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 接下来该怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.27,0:08:40.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对手会让你这种走一步算一步的套路次次得逞吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.74,0:08:43.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光是以机体性能来讲..
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.70,0:08:45.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它具有凌驾于敌人的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.41,0:08:48.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来的事就取决于她了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.91,0:08:52.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果还不是走一步算一步么..
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.68,0:08:53.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也可以这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.67,0:08:57.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以最后问一句吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.69,0:08:58.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请尽管问
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.67,0:09:02.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所谓的“本队”真的会来吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.37,0:09:05.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等那边的战争一结束..立刻赶来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.80,0:09:12.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,头儿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.57,0:09:13.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.10,0:09:15.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机师逃走了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.94,0:09:24.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行了 完全迷路了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.48,0:09:27.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.38,0:09:31.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.68,0:09:35.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？虽然有点像..
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.12,0:09:38.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是有点不一样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.84,0:09:43.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁？请等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.82,0:09:46.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.71,0:09:51.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.32,0:09:53.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实我..
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.04,0:09:55.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迷路了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.26,0:09:59.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也一样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.43,0:10:01.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个~
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.84,0:10:03.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冒昧问一下~
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.92,0:10:04.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您哪位~
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.41,0:10:06.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该说是机师还是..
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.66,0:10:09.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正确的是京乃圆
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.08,0:10:10.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又是？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.95,0:10:12.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫姆奇娜美
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.49,0:10:14.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个..姆奇娜美小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.34,0:10:16.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收到~
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.90,0:10:18.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我去看那边
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.68,0:10:20.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去那边
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.21,0:10:22.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 好的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.55,0:10:24.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.35,0:10:26.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是要我做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.63,0:10:30.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.32,0:10:38.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说..其实我并不是逃跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.95,0:10:40.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行了 你的心情我了解
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.57,0:10:42.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.81,0:10:49.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算我也想多出一份力 而不是把所有重负都推给京乃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.10,0:10:52.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我只能使它飞起来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.59,0:10:55.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个..你在说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.29,0:11:00.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 我..
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.93,0:11:17.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么紧身的..绝对穿不进去啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.15,0:11:21.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来帮我一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.31,0:11:28.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉能行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.68,0:11:30.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.86,0:11:32.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之走到哪算到哪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.29,0:11:34.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还挺明白事的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.57,0:11:36.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷静下来听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.78,0:11:38.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.27,0:11:41.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在位置是大岛东南方100公里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.84,0:11:44.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以2马赫的速度笔直朝我方前进
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.77,0:11:46.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去3分钟之后就会发生接触
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.89,0:11:47.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3..3分钟？！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.77,0:11:51.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尖锥形态时的控制全部交给我们
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.34,0:11:52.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和上一次一样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.41,0:11:55.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只要坐在里面就行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.95,0:11:56.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有一个问题
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.45,0:11:59.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次的直直插入是事故？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.11,0:12:00.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直直插入？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.46,0:12:03.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是指造成变形的那次攻击吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.74,0:12:04.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.15,0:12:05.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是事故
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.09,0:12:06.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是作战计划
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.36,0:12:09.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那..还要用那一招吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.04,0:12:10.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.72,0:12:14.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔..这样啊 我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.83,0:12:16.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,京乃小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.85,0:12:17.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.39,0:12:20.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的肩膀上维系着地球的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.64,0:12:21.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.69,0:12:22.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,万事拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.84,0:12:24.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶！等一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.94,0:12:26.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在才给我这种压力？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.48,0:12:30.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明连东京都没去过突然就是地球？！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.61,0:12:31.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沃克斯·奥拉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.61,0:12:31.11,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,660)}vox aura
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.52,0:12:33.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始连接人工感情系统
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.52,0:12:33.44,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(740,660)}ai emotion system
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.97,0:12:38.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机师心跳数 血压 呼吸频率均处于正常值
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.40,0:12:41.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二号敌机 正在继续加速中
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.84,0:12:42.79,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}上部闸门开启
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.94,0:12:44.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距离沃克斯·奥拉的接敌预计时间大约还有90秒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.94,0:12:44.59,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(420,660)}vox aura
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.09,0:12:46.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人工感情系统运作正常
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.09,0:12:46.57,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(560,660)}ai emotion system
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.44,0:12:49.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未受到来自沃克斯系统的干扰
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.44,0:12:49.08,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(690,660)}vox system
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.36,0:12:50.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,升降轨内清空完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.16,0:12:52.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全系统AllGreen
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.33,0:12:57.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像..突然变得超级紧张
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.73,0:13:02.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沃克斯系统..和上次一样一直处于沉默状态
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.73,0:13:02.74,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(324,660)}vox system
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.40,0:13:06.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我们一起期待她的表现吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.36,0:13:12.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沃克斯·奥拉出击！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.36,0:13:12.76,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(600,660)}vox aura
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.50,0:13:43.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欧比特反应不是阿雷的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.86,0:13:44.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说..
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.21,0:13:45.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沃克斯！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.21,0:13:45.79,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(619,660)}vox
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.62,0:13:51.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前方应该能看见敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.05,0:13:53.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看见了 黑色的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.00,0:13:54.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样上了哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.83,0:13:55.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶！？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.34,0:13:59.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之..撞上去！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.33,0:14:02.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要来么..正合我意！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.04,0:14:22.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么事了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.19,0:14:25.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不清楚 沃克斯系统突然启动
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.19,0:14:25.86,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(625,660)}vox system
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.28,0:14:28.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自动控制模式被取代了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.28,0:14:28.29,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(545,660)}AI·driver mode
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.02,0:14:30.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.65,0:14:32.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意思是尖锥形态的控制权也要给她么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.40,0:14:37.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然适应性不错呢 她和沃克斯·奥拉之间..
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.40,0:14:37.27,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(825,660)}vox aura
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.75,0:14:38.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得好像事不关己似的..
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.76,0:14:41.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各舰进入迎击体系
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.64,0:14:46.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又到了个无所谓的地方..
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.00,0:14:48.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里实在太大了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.89,0:14:50.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到里面去吧 学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.08,0:14:51.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是..
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.63,0:14:56.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？它在干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.82,0:14:58.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在逃？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.97,0:15:11.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底什么情况啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.89,0:15:18.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真家伙的话会怎么出招呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.17,0:15:22.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沃克斯·奥拉 动力输出部件出现异常！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.17,0:15:22.00,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(400,660)}vox aura
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.65,0:15:23.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去的话..
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.69,0:15:32.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机师的情况如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.19,0:15:34.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活体信号正常
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.58,0:15:36.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是机体完全陷入了沉默状态
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.63,0:15:52.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问您要去哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.25,0:15:56.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐的你能做得到吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.38,0:16:14.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs48}现在这位对传说抱以畏惧的大小姐真的能接受得了沃克斯么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.38,0:16:14.07,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1089,660)}vox
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.54,0:16:22.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿雷被这种货色干掉了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.16,0:16:52.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 什么都看不见
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.19,0:17:12.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也是没办法的嘛..
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.43,0:17:14.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从一开始就太乱来了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.89,0:17:17.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然让我当什么机师..
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.38,0:17:30.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.32,0:17:33.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.60,0:17:34.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你现在人在哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.45,0:17:37.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,..在机器人里面
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.25,0:17:39.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.30,0:17:42.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,声音 切换到扩音器上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.22,0:17:44.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？你不吃惊吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.36,0:17:46.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手机居然还能通？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.97,0:17:47.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从哪里打来的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.91,0:17:48.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基地内部
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.25,0:17:53.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你会坐在机器人上面？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.29,0:17:56.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛..各种原因
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.12,0:18:00.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 我有事想问问你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.63,0:18:05.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我十年前在海里溺水的时候有发生什么事吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.67,0:18:08.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说你还记得吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.88,0:18:12.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我记得很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.20,0:18:17.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我那个时候好像和这个机器人见过面呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.33,0:18:18.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌势情况如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.42,0:18:20.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与沃克斯·奥拉距离200
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.42,0:18:20.85,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(615,660)}vox aura
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.34,0:18:22.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那团黑烟之中
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.87,0:18:23.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？她是？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.74,0:18:27.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然在那种地方..
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.69,0:18:29.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是海洋考古学者
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.71,0:18:33.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于沃克斯·奥拉的研究被这里的财团抢走..
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.71,0:18:33.05,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(435,660)}vox aura
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.54,0:18:35.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后就一直在附近晃悠
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.05,0:18:37.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那她是？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.95,0:18:39.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机师的堂姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.78,0:18:42.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于京乃圆登上沃克斯·奥拉持反对意见的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.78,0:18:42.69,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(635,660)}vox aura
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.32,0:18:47.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个机器人很厉害哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.38,0:18:49.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会照我想的去做
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.33,0:18:51.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然一开始很害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.88,0:18:53.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是一下子就抓到了窍门
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.01,0:18:55.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实还蛮快乐的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.48,0:18:57.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在不快乐吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.22,0:19:01.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯..好像有点想太多
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.08,0:19:05.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌势二号与沃克斯·奥拉距离130
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.08,0:19:05.78,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(700,660)}vox aura
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.67,0:19:10.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于我坐上这台机体..出乎我的预料 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.85,0:19:13.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎凝聚着很多人的各种心情
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.97,0:19:18.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我自己是很想去回应他们的感情啊 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.95,0:19:22.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想背叛其中任何一位 可是..
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.75,0:19:27.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像这样考虑了很多之后 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.60,0:19:29.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就变得动弹不得了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.10,0:19:33.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少..臭美了！！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.61,0:19:34.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.39,0:19:34.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.39,0:19:37.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以为自己算老几？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.84,0:19:41.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想做的心情越被动才越让自己动弹不得啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.42,0:19:44.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是自己主动去替他们拼命这种烂好人态度也要不得
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.75,0:19:47.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是自己决定要做
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.93,0:19:49.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么自己说出的话总要自己来承担责任的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.52,0:19:51.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果这都不要的话..
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.69,0:19:54.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,运动服部什么的赶紧废了吧！！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.41,0:20:04.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火大了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.35,0:20:07.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您说的正是 可能无限接近正确答案
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.11,0:20:10.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是被姐姐你一说..
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.66,0:20:13.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就超让人火大！！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.72,0:20:15.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不甘心！！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.71,0:20:23.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和敌势的距离20
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.30,0:20:39.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距离 10
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.41,0:20:41.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,9..8..
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.50,0:20:42.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么 给我动啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.63,0:20:46.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,7..6..5..4..
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.52,0:20:48.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沃克斯系统启动
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.52,0:20:48.55,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(596,660)}vox system
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.12,0:20:49.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和敌势的距离是？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.10,0:20:51.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,0..
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.26,0:21:13.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.75,0:21:16.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 发生什么事了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.92,0:21:20.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不明机体突破大气层
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.65,0:21:21.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地点是？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.07,0:21:22.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.98,0:21:26.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.17,0:21:39.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被夹击了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.68,0:21:42.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基里乌斯..你..
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.30,0:21:47.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能继续袖手旁观下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.18,0:21:49.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死的时候要三个人一起！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.42,0:23:31.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可要上了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.42,0:23:31.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要上什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.10,0:23:33.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说要上了就要上
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.42,0:23:34.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说要上什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.26,0:23:36.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说了要上就一定上得彻底才是我的主义
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.07,0:23:38.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以在问你要上什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.09,0:23:39.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上钩了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.59,0:23:40.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 上钩了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.74,0:23:41.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.55,0:23:42.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.27,0:23:44.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我..被抓住了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.28,0:23:44.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好逊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.88,0:23:45.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说了什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.53,0:23:46.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说你丢脸
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.76,0:23:47.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.26,0:23:48.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不需要说的那么清楚啦！
